{{main|Heroes of the Environment}} '''Heroes of the Environment''' is a list published in [[Time Magazine]]. The inaugural list was published in October 2007.<ref name="timecover">[http://www.time.com/time/specials/2007/article/0,28804,1663317_1672378_1672379,00.html Heroes of the Environment - TIME] - Cover story.</ref> The list contains 43 entries, individuals or groups that have contributed substantially to the preservation of environment, and is divided into four categories: Leaders & Visionaries, Activists, Scientists & Innovators, and [[Business magnate|Moguls]] & Entrepreneurs.
The list has been commented and discussed worldwide, in newspapers or by organizations.<ref>{{cite news|last1=Aldred|first1=Jessica|title=Heroes of the environment|url=https://www.theguardian.com/environment/blog/2007/oct/22/heroesoftheenvironment|accessdate=10 May 2018|work=[[The Guardian]]|date=22 October 2007}}</ref><ref> {{cite web |title=Time magazine names eco-heroes |url=https://www.edie.net/news/0/Time-magazine-names-eco-heroes/13720/ |date=31 October 2007 |website=edie.net }}</ref><ref> {{cite web |title=Environmental Heroes -- Wang Canfa and Zhang Jingjing |url=https://www.elaw.org/environmental-heroes-wang-canfa-and-zhang-jingjing |publisher=[[Environmental Law Alliance Worldwide]] |access-date=10 May 2018 |website=elaw.org }}</ref><ref> {{cite web |title=Israeli activist named one of TIME’s ‘Heroes of the Environment’ |url=https://www.israel21c.org/israeli-activist-named-one-of-times-heroes-of-the-environment/ |first=David |last=Brinn |date=October 24, 2007 |access-date=10 May 2018 |website=israel21c.org }}</ref><ref> {{cite news |title=Kåret til miljøhelt i Time |url=https://www.aftenposten.no/norge/i/pp1oG/Karet-til-miljohelt-i-Time |first=Elisabeth |last=Rodum |date=19 October 2007 |language=Norwegian |newspaper=[[Aftenposten]] }}</ref><ref> {{cite web |title=Bellona’s President “Hero of the environment” in TIME magazine |url=http://bellona.org/news/climate-change/2007-10-bellonas-president-hero-of-the-environment-in-time-magazine |first=Anne Karin |last=Sæther |date=19 October 2007 |language=Norwegian |publisher=[[Bellona Foundation]] |website=bellona.org }}</ref>
